// Semantic direction:
// equal, greater, and less extend compute from arithmetic into comparison.
// boolean gives comparison results a primitive truth-bearing runtime form.

// Primitive flow:
// value + expression + operator + comparison
// -> boolean
// -> branch/select
// -> updated + output

// This marks the transition from arithmetic computation
